ed in structures that were crack-free and resisted fracture\nduring thermal shock testing. Broadly, the additive manufacturing approach\npresented could be useful for the production of many UHTC carbides that might\notherwise be incompatible with prevailing AM techniques that do not include\nreaction synthesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2022 19:40:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2022 00:43:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 02:38:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
