 model\naccurately predicted the test data. Conclusions: The developed model resulted\nin highly accurate predictions for any ion-target combination across the whole\nparticle energy spectrum. The associated model can serve as a universal tool to\ngenerate the stopping power data in a wide range of cases, regardless of the\navailability of experimental data or reliable theoretical equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Jul 2022 14:15:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
